147 POKE$D013,0:WAIT$D013,1
148 POKE 1024 + RND(1) * 1000, RND(1) * 109 + 31
160 GETA$:IFA$=""THEN78
170 END
500 POKE $D800 + RND(1) * 40, 31
510 G=0
520 RETURN
